123
00:10:04,491 --> 00:10:16,500
mir ho'mir aroy- aroys gebrengen a gantse lift hot es geheysn, azoy vi a shtibl geboyt, az mir veln'mir geyn oyf Yisroel ot zol'mir efhser hobn vu tsu hobn vu tsu shlofn, nisht untern, vayl demolts gezogt nishto vu tsu voynen un

