00:10:25,033 --> 00:10:34,348
m'vet undz gornisht tun, un m'vet undz batsoln hunderter hunderter krone, ikh gedenk nisht vifl,

126
00:10:34,348 --> 00:10:37,340
m'zol'mir avekshikn vayl m'vet es say vi say trefn.

