136
00:11:20,445 --> 00:11:29,180
iz aropgekumen zibn F.B.I., un m'hot mikh un mayn man opgehaltn,

137
00:11:29,237 --> 00:11:39,271
far di kinder, di tsvey kinder, hot men arop geshtelt a a vakh un m'hot adurkhgezukht dos hoyz.

138
00:11:39,598 --> 00:11:41,836
m'hot tsenumen ales.

139
00:11:42,855 --> 00:11:48,738
un vi ikh hob gezogt di gutskeyt fun mayne eltern iz demolts vayter ge- baygeshtanen far mir.

140
00:11:48,795 --> 00:11:55,134
vayl ikh bin aheymgekumen, a nakht, in der nakht fun Prag,

141
00:11:55,326 --> 00:12:00,399
