144
00:12:12,501 --> 00:12:17,915
hob ikh gefilt m'geyt mir nokh. UNK nokhgegangen, nokhgegangen,

145
00:12:18,664 --> 00:12:23,214
bin ikh arayngelofn in a STORE, un ikh hob mir gekoyft an ander hitl.

146
00:12:23,895 --> 00:12:30,436
kum ikh aroys, der mentsh shteyt vayter farn STORE, un m- un un vu ikh gey.

147
00:12:30,612 --> 00:12:35,196
ikh hob gebroykht aheymtsugeyn grod fun Prag oyf Sviskepotragi,

148
00:12:35,590 --> 00:12:39,585
bin ikh genumen an andern tsug, a taksi,

149
00:12:39,585 --> 00:12:44,269
un gekumen durkh an andern veg, durkh Bratislava Otozhinina,

150
00:12:44,269 --> 00:12:49,522
