155
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:21,956
bad-tsimer in koymen arayn. dort vu der BOILER hot zikh geheytst.

156
00:13:24,139 --> 00:13:26,327
arayngevorfn azoy s'nisht gevezn.

157
00:13:26,637 --> 00:13:30,995
un vi ikh shtey un vart, m'geyt'mir tsu tsum pakn,

158
00:13:30,995 --> 00:13:35,709
der F.B.I. fun Bratislava iz ongekumen mit a shvartse kar,

159
00:13:36,154 --> 00:13:38,831
un m'makht undz a ⟨hoyz-unterzukung⟩,

160
00:13:39,478 --> 00:13:43,556
un m'shtelt zikh aroyf oyf der vane,

161
00:13:43,613 --> 00:13:46,881
⟨gekakhelte⟩ vane shoyn demolts hob- ho'mir undz gehat,

162
00:13:47,022 --> 00:13:53,523
